# Secrets template for Zigbee Temperature Sensor
#
# Pure Zigbee devices do not need WiFi credentials, API keys, or OTA
# passwords. This file is included only for consistency with other Aurora
# examples; you can delete it if you prefer.
#
# Copy to secrets.yaml if you decide to add WiFi (for example to bridge
# the device with the ESPHome API alongside Zigbee).
